data.description: Welcome to Portofino Lakes,Large 2 Story, Lake Front home in gated Community, 2500 Sq FT of living space with 5 Beds/3 baths/2 car garage, 1 bedroom and full bath downstairs. Dramatic high ceiling greets you at the front door. Very roomy eat-in kitchen attached to family room with gorgeous lake view to enjoy your morning coffee. Bring your large family - there is plenty of room! The home has vaulted ceilings, tile floors in living areas downstairs and carpeted upstairs and equipped w hurricane shutters. Master bedroom with walk in closet, tub& shower w dual sinks. The community offers Gym, Pool, Security, lawn maintenance. Great Location,very close to Turnpike.*SHOWING TIMES ARE LIMITED TO EARLY MORNINGS DURING THE WEEK AND WEEKENDS AFTER 11AM-530 PM*Pictures are accurate, layout included.
